{"timestamp":"2026-06-19T05:34:18.930Z","type":"tool","initiativeId":"implement-directory-v2-compatibility","step":"IDLE","details":{"toolName":"apply_patch","args":{"patchText":"*** Begin Patch\n*** Add File: /Users/bbaaxx/Code/projects/openagent-mdocs/harness-mdocs/tests/fixtures/directory-v2-mdocs/mdocs/SCHEMA.md\n+# mdocs Schema\n+\n+Directory-style initiatives use `initiatives/<slug>/_status.md`.\n+\n*** Add File: /Users/bbaaxx/Code/projects/openagent-mdocs/harness-mdocs/tests/fixtures/directory-v2-mdocs/mdocs/initiatives/example-active/_status.md\n+---\n+id: example-active\n+title: Example Active\n+status: active\n+started: 2026-01-01\n+tags: [compatibility]\n+---\n+\n+Example directory-v2 initiative.\n+\n*** Add File: /Users/bbaaxx/Code/projects/openagent-mdocs/harness-mdocs/tests/fixtures/directory-v2-mdocs/mdocs/initiatives/INDEX.md\n+# Initiatives\n+\n+- **Example Active** (active) — `example-active/` — 2026-01-01 — [compatibility]\n+\n*** Add File: /Users/bbaaxx/Code/projects/openagent-mdocs/harness-mdocs/tests/fixtures/directory-v2-mdocs/mdocs/wiki/index.md\n+# Wiki\n+\n+Canonical lowercase index. Must not be overwritten.\n+\n+- [System Page](systems/system-page.md)\n+\n*** Add File: /Users/bbaaxx/Code/projects/openagent-mdocs/harness-mdocs/tests/fixtures/directory-v2-mdocs/mdocs/wiki/systems/system-page.md\n+---\n+id: system-page\n+title: System Page\n+category: systems\n+updated: 2026-01-01\n+tags: [compatibility]\n+lifecycle: stable\n+sources: [example-active]\n+---\n+\n+Stable system note.\n+\n*** Add File: /Users/bbaaxx/Code/projects/openagent-mdocs/harness-mdocs/tests/fixtures/directory-v2-mdocs/mdocs/_obsidian/README.md\n+# Obsidian visibility layer\n+\n+Not canonical mdocs data.\n+\n*** Update File: /Users/bbaaxx/Code/projects/openagent-mdocs/harness-mdocs/tests/core/compatibility.test.ts\n@@\n test('existing mdocs fixture is readable without destructive initialization', () => {\n@@\n   expect(after).toBe(before);\n });\n+\n+test('directory-v2 fixture is readable without uppercase wiki index', () => {\n+  const projectDir = fs.mkdtempSync(path.join(os.tmpdir(), 'harness-mdocs-dirv2-'));\n+  const fixtureRoot = path.resolve(__dirname, '../fixtures/directory-v2-mdocs');\n+  copyDir(fixtureRoot, projectDir);\n+\n+  const wikiIndexPath = path.join(projectDir, 'mdocs', 'wiki', 'index.md');\n+  const before = fs.readFileSync(wikiIndexPath, 'utf8');\n+  const core = createMdocsCore(projectDir);\n+  const initResult = core.lifecycle.ensureInitialized();\n+  const after = fs.readFileSync(wikiIndexPath, 'utf8');\n+\n+  expect(initResult).toEqual({ initialized: false, bootstrapInitiativeCreated: false });\n+  expect(core.managers.mdocs.exists()).toBe(true);\n+  expect(after).toBe(before);\n+  expect(fs.existsSync(path.join(projectDir, 'mdocs', 'wiki', 'INDEX.md'))).toBe(false);\n+});\n+\n+test('index sync is safe for directory-v2 external wiki index', () => {\n+  const projectDir = fs.mkdtempSync(path.join(os.tmpdir(), 'harness-mdocs-dirv2-sync-'));\n+  const fixtureRoot = path.resolve(__dirname, '../fixtures/directory-v2-mdocs');\n+  copyDir(fixtureRoot, projectDir);\n+\n+  const wikiIndexPath = path.join(projectDir, 'mdocs', 'wiki', 'index.md');\n+  const before = fs.readFileSync(wikiIndexPath, 'utf8');\n+  const core = createMdocsCore(projectDir);\n+  const result = core.managers.wiki.syncIndices();\n+  const after = fs.readFileSync(wikiIndexPath, 'utf8');\n+\n+  expect(result).toEqual([]);\n+  expect(after).toBe(before);\n+  expect(fs.existsSync(path.join(projectDir, 'mdocs', 'wiki', 'INDEX.md'))).toBe(false);\n+  expect(fs.existsSync(path.join(projectDir, 'mdocs', 'wiki', 'systems', 'INDEX.md'))).toBe(false);\n+});\n+\n+test('directory-v2 index consistency does not require generated uppercase indices', () => {\n+  const projectDir = fs.mkdtempSync(path.join(os.tmpdir(), 'harness-mdocs-dirv2-check-'));\n+  const fixtureRoot = path.resolve(__dirname, '../fixtures/directory-v2-mdocs');\n+  copyDir(fixtureRoot, projectDir);\n+\n+  const core = createMdocsCore(projectDir);\n+  const result = core.managers.wiki.checkConsistency();\n+\n+  expect(result).toEqual({ consistent: true, missing: [], orphans: [], stale: false });\n+});\n*** End Patch"}}}
