{"timestamp":"2026-06-19T05:35:59.444Z","type":"tool","initiativeId":"implement-directory-v2-compatibility","step":"IDLE","details":{"toolName":"apply_patch","args":{"patchText":"*** Begin Patch\n*** Update File: /Users/bbaaxx/Code/projects/openagent-mdocs/harness-mdocs/src/core/contract.ts\n@@\n function safeExists(filePath: string): boolean {\n@@\n }\n+\n+function hasExactChild(parentDir: string, childName: string): boolean {\n+  if (!safeExists(parentDir)) return false;\n+  try {\n+    return fs.readdirSync(parentDir).includes(childName);\n+  } catch {\n+    return false;\n+  }\n+}\n@@\n-  const lowercaseWikiIndex = safeExists(path.join(wikiDir, 'index.md'));\n-  const uppercaseWikiIndex = safeExists(path.join(wikiDir, 'INDEX.md'));\n+  const lowercaseWikiIndex = hasExactChild(wikiDir, 'index.md');\n+  const uppercaseWikiIndex = hasExactChild(wikiDir, 'INDEX.md');\n*** End Patch"}}}
