{"timestamp":"2026-06-19T05:53:42.926Z","type":"tool","initiativeId":"implement-directory-v2-compatibility","step":"IDLE","details":{"toolName":"apply_patch","args":{"patchText":"*** Begin Patch\n*** Add File: /Users/bbaaxx/Code/projects/openagent-mdocs/harness-mdocs/tests/fixtures/directory-v2-mdocs/mdocs/initiatives/example-complete/_status.md\n+---\n+id: example-complete\n+title: Example Complete\n+status: complete\n+started: 2026-01-02\n+completed: 2026-01-03\n+tags: [compatibility, done]\n+---\n+\n+Completed directory-v2 initiative.\n+\n*** Add File: /Users/bbaaxx/Code/projects/openagent-mdocs/harness-mdocs/tests/fixtures/directory-v2-mdocs/mdocs/initiatives/_archive/example-archived/_status.md\n+---\n+id: example-archived\n+title: Example Archived\n+status: archived\n+started: 2025-12-01\n+completed: 2025-12-02\n+tags: [compatibility, archived]\n+---\n+\n+Archived directory-v2 initiative.\n+\n*** Add File: /Users/bbaaxx/Code/projects/openagent-mdocs/harness-mdocs/tests/fixtures/directory-v2-mdocs/mdocs/initiatives/legacy-flat--2026-01-04.md\n+---\n+id: \"legacy-flat\"\n+title: \"Legacy Flat\"\n+status: \"active\"\n+created: \"2026-01-04\"\n+updated: \"2026-01-04\"\n+owner: \"system\"\n+tags: [\"legacy\"]\n+related_wiki: []\n+---\n+\n+## Objective\n+Legacy flat initiative in directory-v2 repo.\n+\n+## Plan\n+- [ ] Keep readable\n+\n+## Progress Log\n+\n+## Artifacts\n+\n*** Update File: /Users/bbaaxx/Code/projects/openagent-mdocs/harness-mdocs/tests/core/compatibility.test.ts\n@@\n test('directory-v2 detection avoids generated indices when lowercase index is absent', () => {\n@@\n   expect(contract.wikiIndexOwner).toBe('none');\n });\n+\n+test('directory-v2 initiatives are readable by lookup, search, and aliases', () => {\n+  const projectDir = fs.mkdtempSync(path.join(os.tmpdir(), 'harness-mdocs-dirv2-read-'));\n+  const fixtureRoot = path.resolve(__dirname, '../fixtures/directory-v2-mdocs');\n+  copyDir(fixtureRoot, projectDir);\n+  const core = createMdocsCore(projectDir);\n+\n+  expect(core.managers.initiatives.findById('example-active')?.title).toBe('Example Active');\n+  expect(core.managers.initiatives.findById('example-complete')?.status).toBe('done');\n+  expect(core.managers.initiatives.findById('legacy-flat')?.title).toBe('Legacy Flat');\n+  expect(core.managers.initiatives.findById('example-archived')).toBeNull();\n+  expect(core.managers.initiatives.list(true).some(initiative => initiative.id === 'example-archived')).toBe(true);\n+  expect(core.managers.initiatives.findByQuery('example-active')?.key).toBe('example-active');\n+});\n+\n+test('directory-v2 lookup and search include directory initiatives', () => {\n+  const projectDir = fs.mkdtempSync(path.join(os.tmpdir(), 'harness-mdocs-dirv2-ops-'));\n+  const fixtureRoot = path.resolve(__dirname, '../fixtures/directory-v2-mdocs');\n+  copyDir(fixtureRoot, projectDir);\n+  const core = createMdocsCore(projectDir);\n+\n+  expect(core.commands.execute('initiative.lookup' as any, { query: 'example-active' } as any)).toMatchObject({\n+    id: 'example-active',\n+    filename: 'example-active'\n+  });\n+  expect(core.managers.search.query('directory-v2 initiative').some(result => result.id === 'example-active')).toBe(true);\n+});\n*** End Patch"}}}
